Seamless Proctoring, Anytime & Anywhere Across the Globe
Live proctoring Live proctoring provides real-time monitoring of online exams by trained proctors, ensuring the highest level of exam integrity and security. The system ensures seamless communication between test-takers and proctors, offering immediate technical support when needed. Live proctoring eliminates geographical barriers, allowing institutions worldwide to conduct secure online exams while upholding academic honesty and maintaining trust in remote assessments.

4o
Global Access Al-powered online proctoring is built with flexibility in mind. Students can take their exam anytime, no complicated pre-scheduling required. No need to wait in a queue for an extended period of time or pay increased fees to take their exam now. No need for students to visit a library, testing center, or campus to finish a test. They receive the flexibility of online testing, while Al-powered online proctoring ensures an equitable testing environment for all.
Simple & Flexible Al-powered online proctoring 's online proctoring solutions allow students to take exams from anywhere with a standard microphone, webcam, and an internet connection. With one-click sign-on and Al-powered online proctoring allows students to stay focused on their quizzes, assessments, exams, mid-terms, and finals, without worrying about technical issues.
MANU Visage is an advanced proctoring solution designed to revolutionize online assessments with cutting-edge face recognition, emotion detection, and identity verification. Our system ensures secure, fair, and seamless examinations by leveraging AI-driven monitoring, real-time analysis, and automated proctoring. Built for academic institutions and organizations, MANU Visage enhances exam integrity while providing a smooth test-taking experience. Redefining Online Exam Integrity
